'''{{lang|en|Apple Music}}'''（'''苹果音乐'''）是[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]于[[2015年|2015年]]6月30日推出的一款在线[[音乐流媒体|音乐流媒体]]服务。此项服务的用户可以根据自己的选择，在设备上点播歌曲。{{lang|en|Apple Music}}服务中还包括了网络电台“{{lang|en|'''Apple Music 1'''}}”（曾用名为Beats 1{{noteTag|1=2020年8月18日，苹果宣布Beats 1更名为Apple Music 1<ref>{{cite web |title=Apple announces Apple Music radio |url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2020/08/apple-announces-apple-music-radio/ |website=Apple Newsroom |accessdate=2020-08-19 |language=en |date=2020-08-18 |archive-date=2020-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819001806/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2020/08/apple-announces-apple-music-radio/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}）。用户可免费试用三个月{{notetag|1=後只剩一個月}}，之后转为收费服务。{{lang|en|Apple Music}}能够根据用户的口味向用户推荐音乐，整个服务也整合到了{{lang|en|[[Siri|Siri]]}}语音控制服务中。2016年时，这项服务支持全球113个国家和地区，是全球第二大流媒体音乐服务，次于[[Spotify|Spotify]]。其在不同国家的收费有所差别，而且在部分地区不提供{{Lang|en|Apple Music 1}}电台服务。

{{Lang|en|Apple Music}}服务发布之后一度因操作和界面复杂而引发部分用户不满。但总体上，媒体和用户普遍认为其功能十分优秀，对服务给出正面评价。其中，根据用户爱好推荐的音乐中加入了音乐专家的手工选择，推荐结果更加准确，被认为是{{Lang|en|Apple Music}}的巨大优势；{{lang|en|Apple Music 1}}电台也被认为是服务的焦点所在。这两项服务收到了大量正面评价。{{lang|en|Connect}}平台为歌手提供与用户交流的平台，虽得到部分好评，但未能获得用户的广泛认可。{{lang|en|Apple Music}}推出之初计划在试用期的三个月内不支付[[版税|版税]]，遭到歌手的抗议和抵制，然而争议最终以苹果公司修改版税支付政策而告终。此外苹果公司推出这项服务的过程中可能涉嫌不当竞争，也引起了美国联邦贸易委员会和相关产业的关注。

== 功能概况 ==
2015年6月，苹果公司在[[苹果公司全球软件开发者年会|全球软件开发者年会]]上宣布，将于6月30日正式推出{{lang|en|Apple Music}}这项服务，试用期三个月内免费使用。针对美国用户，三个月之后将对个人用户每月收费9.99[[美元|美元]]，对不超过6人的家庭用户每月收费14.99美元。<ref name="NYT WWDC">{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/apple-wwdc-2015/apple-music-does-everything-apple-says/ |accessdate=2015-07-19 |title=Apple W.W.D.C. 2015: iOS 9, Apple Pay and Other Announcements |date=2015-06-08 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |deadurl=no |archive-date=2015-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622124220/http://www.nytimes.com/live/apple-wwdc-2015/apple-music-does-everything-apple-says/ }}</ref>服务正式推出后，在不同国家的具体价格有所不同：首发推出的[[印度|印度]]服务对个人用户每月收费仅需120[[印度卢比|卢比]]（约1.83美元）；9月30日开通的[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]服务对个人用户每月收费10元[[人民币|人民币]]（约1.57美元），对高校学生每月收费5元人民币（约0.786美元），成为全球最低的价格；[[英国|英国]]个人用户的收费则高至每月9.99[[英镑|英镑]]（约15.16美元）。{{noteTag|1=不同货币之间的折算以2015年9月末的汇率为准。}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.magneticmag.com/2015/10/apple-music-launches-in-china-for-a-fraction-of-the-price/|title=APPLE MUSIC LAUNCHES IN CHINA AT IT'S LOWEST COST WORLDWIDE|work=Magnetic Mag|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-11-11|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117024030/http://www.magneticmag.com/2015/10/apple-music-launches-in-china-for-a-fraction-of-the-price/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/3944572/apple-music-pricing/|work=TIME|title=Apple Music Is Cheaper Depending on Where You Live|date=2015-07-02|accessdate=2015-11-11|first=Victor|last=Luckerson|archive-date=2015-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151112110837/http://time.com/3944572/apple-music-pricing/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://money.cnn.com/2015/09/30/technology/apple-music-china/|title=Apple Music is coming to China - and it's cheap|work=CNN Money|date=2015-09-30|accessdate=2015-11-11|first=Rob|last=McLean|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117031151/http://money.cnn.com/2015/09/30/technology/apple-music-china/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

用户使用时，在设备上选择音乐，就可通过[[流媒体|流媒体]]收听，也可保存在设备上供离线使用。用户可以选择自己喜爱的音乐风格，也可以点击“喜欢”（{{Lang|en|"Like"}}）按键标记自己喜欢的音乐，{{lang|en|Apple Music}}可根据用户喜欢的音乐口味提供推荐。这项服务的收费价格以及歌曲库的大小和其他音乐流媒体服务相似，但其独特之处在于附加的功能以及独家提供的音乐内容。{{lang|en|Apple Music}}亦可以通过{{lang|en|[[Siri|Siri]]}}进行语音控制，用户可以通过{{lang|en|Siri}}直接选择特定的歌曲播放，也可选择播放符合某种条件的歌曲。<ref name="Verge: announce">{{cite web |url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/8/8729481/apple-music-streaming-service-wwdc-15 |title=Apple announces its streaming music service, Apple Music |accessdate=2015-07-19 |date=2015-06-08 |work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Z8hZFUn5?url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/8/8729481/apple-music-streaming-service-wwdc-15 |archivedate=2015-06-08 |last1=Popper |first1=Ben |last2=Singleton |first2=Micah |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Ars: next chapter" />{{Lang|en|[[iOS_10|iOS 10]]}}之后的{{lang|en|Apple Music}}在播放中还会显示歌曲的歌词<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=http://sspai.com/34532|title=WWDC 发布了 iOS 10 和 macOS Sierra 的一大堆新东西，都整理在这儿了|accessdate=2016-06-14|author=|date=2016-06-14|publisher=少数派|archive-date=2016-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617112613/http://sspai.com/34532|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/6/13/11903956/apple-music-update-itunes-redesign-announced-wwdc-2016|title=Apple Music gets 'redesigned from the ground up'|accessdate=2016-06-14|author=|date=2016-06-13|last=Statt|first=Nick|publisher=The Verge|archive-date=2016-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160614122903/http://www.theverge.com/2016/6/13/11903956/apple-music-update-itunes-redesign-announced-wwdc-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{lang|en|Apple Music}}还包含了著名艺人负责的网络电台服务，其首个电台“{{lang|en|Beats 1}}”在超过100个国家提供24小时不间断的音乐广播，绝大多数拥有{{lang|en|Apple Music}}服务的国家和地区都可以收听。电台由三位DJ主播：曾在[[BBC廣播一台|BBC廣播一台]]工作的DJ{{le|赞恩·洛|Zane Lowe}}负责在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]主播，[[嘻哈|嘻哈]]DJ{{le|埃夫罗·达登|Ebro Darden}}在[[纽约|纽约]]主播，英国DJ{{le|朱莉·阿德努加|Julie Adenuga}}则负责在[[伦敦|伦敦]]主播。<ref name=apple/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2015/jul/18/beats-1-david-hepworth|title=Beats 1: it’s radio but not as you know it|work=The Guardian|date=2015-07-18|accessdate=2015-07-19|first=David|last=Hepworth|archive-date=2015-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150718153923/http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2015/jul/18/beats-1-david-hepworth|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com.au/what-people-think-about-apple-beats-1-radio-station-music-2015-7|title=Here's what people are saying about Beats 1, Apple's new global radio station|date=2015-07-18|accessdate=2015-07-19|first=Rob|last=Price|work=Business Insider|archive-date=2015-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150720041515/http://www.businessinsider.com.au/what-people-think-about-apple-beats-1-radio-station-music-2015-7|dead-url=no}}</ref>苹果公司原有的{{lang|en|[[iTunes_Radio|iTunes Radio]]}}网络电台服务也整合到{{Lang|en|Apple Music}}的付费服务中，同时更名为{{Lang|en|Apple Music Radio}}；原有的免费{{Lang|en|iTunes Radio}}服务则于2016年1月被关闭，但{{lang|en|Beats 1}}电台则可以供用户免费收听。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://arstechnica.com/apple/2016/01/apple-axes-free-itunes-radio-service-directs-listeners-to-beats-1-instead/|title = Apple axes free iTunes Radio service, directs listeners to Beats 1 instead|last = Cunningham|first = Andrew|date = 2016-01-17|work = Arstechnica|accessdate = 2016-02-05|archive-date = 2016-02-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160205132757/http://arstechnica.com/apple/2016/01/apple-axes-free-itunes-radio-service-directs-listeners-to-beats-1-instead/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://mashable.com/2016/01/29/apple-itunes-radio-discontinued/|title = Apple's free iTunes Radio is no more|last = Schroeder|first = Stan|date = 2016-01-29|work = Mashable|accessdate = 2016-02-05|archive-date = 2016-02-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160205121916/http://mashable.com/2016/01/29/apple-itunes-radio-discontinued/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://mashable.com/2016/01/15/itunes-radio-apple-music/|title = iTunes Radio will no longer be free|last = Bell|first = Karissa|date = 2016-01-16|work = Mashable|accessdate = 2016-02-05|archive-date = 2016-02-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160205122154/http://mashable.com/2016/01/15/itunes-radio-apple-music/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

此外，{{lang|en|Apple Music}}还提供另一项服务“{{lang|en|Connect}}”。这是供艺人向听众分享音乐的博客平台，其中的一部分音乐将是这个平台独家提供的。<ref name="Verge: announce"/><ref name="Ars: next chapter">{{cite web |url=http://arstechnica.com/apple/2015/06/apple-music-is-the-next-chapter-in-music/ |accessdate=2015-07-19 |title=Apple Music is 'the next chapter in music,' debuts June 30 |last1=Machkovech |first1=Sam |date=2015-06-08 |work=Ars Technica |publisher=Condé Nast Digital |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ZG1MHngK?url=http://arstechnica.com/apple/2015/06/apple-music-is-the-next-chapter-in-music/ |archivedate=2015-06-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>歌手[[德雷克_(歌手)|德雷克]]在全球软件开发者年会现场演示{{lang|en|Connect}}平台的操作时，就宣布将通过这一平台发布一张新专辑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/8/8747901/wwdc2015-apple-music-connect-drake-new-album|title=Drake to release his next album using Apple Music's new Connect feature|accessdate=2015-07-19|date=2015-06-08|last=Opam|first=Kwame|work=The Verge|archive-date=2015-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717073010/http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/8/8747901/wwdc2015-apple-music-connect-drake-new-album|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而苹果公司也强调未签约的独立艺人同样可以参与到{{lang|en|Connect}}平台中<ref name="Ars: next chapter"/>。但此项功能推出后并不受欢迎。苹果公司于2016年更新的{{lang|en|iOS 10}}中移除了{{lang|en|Apple Music}}用户界面中的{{lang|en|Connect}}标签页，之后于2018年12月停止了此项服务。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Welch |first1=Chris |title=Apple is shutting down Apple Music's rarely-used Connect feature |url=https://www.theverge.com/2018/12/13/18139837/apple-music-connect-social-network-feature-discontinued |accessdate=2019-01-25 |work=The Verge |date=2018-12-13 |archive-date=2019-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190125183250/https://www.theverge.com/2018/12/13/18139837/apple-music-connect-social-network-feature-discontinued |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Roettgers |first1=Janko |last2=Roettgers |first2=Janko |title=Apple Music Phases Out Connect Social Feed |url=https://variety.com/2018/digital/news/apple-music-connect-dsicontinued-1203089337/ |accessdate=2019-01-25 |work=Variety |date=2018-12-13 |archive-date=2019-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190102095444/https://variety.com/2018/digital/news/apple-music-connect-dsicontinued-1203089337/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

{{lang|en|Apple Music}}的页面中包含了多个标签页。“为你推荐”（{{lang|en|"For You"}}）标签页中包含了为用户推荐的音乐，其推荐算法之外还有音乐专家的手工选择对此进行补充。在“我的音乐”（{{lang|en|"My Music"}}）标签页中则显示了用户已购买的歌曲和可以通过在线流媒体收听的歌曲。<ref name="Ars: next chapter"/>“广播”（{{Lang|en|"Radio"}}）标签页中收录了{{lang|en|Beats 1}}和{{Lang|en|Apple Music Radio}}服务。<ref name=":3" /><ref name=":4" />。

{{lang|en|Apple Music}}支持的使用设备包括：{{lang|en|[[iOS_8|iOS 8.4]]}}及更高版本的设备，{{lang|en|[[iTunes|iTunes]]}} 12.2或更高版本（支持{{lang|en|[[OS_X_Mavericks|OS X Mavericks]]}}及更高版本、{{lang|en|[[Windows_7|Windows 7]]}}及更高版本）、{{lang|en|[[Apple_Watch|Apple Watch]]}}、{{lang|en|[[Apple_TV|Apple TV]]}}以及{{lang|en|[[Android_5.0|Android 5.0]]}}及更高版本的设备。对于没有安装相关应用程序的设备，可以通过[[网页浏览器|网页浏览器]]使用网页版的Apple Music。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple Music launches a public beta on the web|url=https://social.techcrunch.com/2019/09/05/apple-music-launches-a-public-beta-on-the-web/|accessdate=2020-04-17|work=TechCrunch|language=en-US}}</ref>{{lang|en|Beats 1}}电台只能通过{{lang|en|iOS}}设备或有效{{lang|en|[[Apple_ID|Apple ID]]}}登录的{{lang|en|iTunes}}收听，其内容通过{{lang|en|{{le|FairPlay|FairPlay}}}}[[数字版权管理|数字版权管理]]技术进行加密以确保此项限制。<ref name=apple/><ref name="TechCrunch">{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2015/06/30/apple-music-now-available-on-the-mac-via-itunes|title=Apple Music Now Available On The Mac Via iTunes|first=Darrell|last=Etherington|work=TechCrunch|date=2015-06-30|accessdate=2015-07-19|archive-date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721073039/http://techcrunch.com/2015/06/30/apple-music-now-available-on-the-mac-via-itunes/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2015/07/01/an-unofficial-web-stream-for-apple-musics-beats1-radio-lets-android-users-tune-in/|title=Developer Finds A Web Stream For Apple Music’s Beats 1 Radio That Lets Android Users Tune In|work=TechCrunch|date=2015-07-01|accessdate=2015-07-19|first=Sarah|last=Perez|archive-date=2015-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150720231445/http://techcrunch.com/2015/07/01/an-unofficial-web-stream-for-apple-musics-beats1-radio-lets-android-users-tune-in/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mcelhearn.com/the-real-difference-between-itunes-match-and-icloud-music-library-drm/|title=The Real Difference Between iTunes Match and iCloud Music Library: DRM|work=Mcelhearn.com|date=2015-07-01|accessdate=2015-07-19|first=Kirk|last=McElhearn|archive-date=2015-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717070127/http://www.mcelhearn.com/the-real-difference-between-itunes-match-and-icloud-music-library-drm/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Android">{{cite web|1=|url=http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2015-11/10/apple-music-android|title=Apple Music launches on Android|work=Wired|date=2015-11-10|accessdate=2015-11-11|first=Michael|last=Rundle|archive-date=2015-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151110223813/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2015-11/10/apple-music-android|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Android2">{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/11/10/9705434/apple-music-android-launch|title=Apple Music launches on Android|work=The Verge|date=2015-11-10|accessdate=2015-11-11|first=Jacob|last=Kastrenakes|archive-date=2015-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151112020728/http://www.theverge.com/2015/11/10/9705434/apple-music-android-launch|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2015/11/10/apple-music-beta-android/|title=Apple Music arrives on Android, bringing your iTunes library along for the ride|work=Mashable|date=2015-11-11|accessdate=2015-11-11|first=Christina|last=Warren|archive-date=2015-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151112193404/http://mashable.com/2015/11/10/apple-music-beta-android/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite web|url=http://www.techradar.com/how-to/phone-and-communications/the-complete-guide-to-apple-music-1311497|title=The complete guide to Apple Music|work=TechRadar|date=2016-01-07|accessdate=2016-06-05|archive-date=2016-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160601231628/http://www.techradar.com/how-to/phone-and-communications/the-complete-guide-to-apple-music-1311497|dead-url=no}}</ref>

