== 发展历史 ==
=== 服务上线和扩张 ===
在{{lang|en|Apple Music}}之前，苹果公司的{{lang|en|[[iPod|iPod]]}}和{{lang|en|[[iTunes|iTunes]]}}已经“变革了数字音乐”<ref name="Verge: announce"/>。苹果公司前首席执行官[[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史蒂夫·乔布斯]]最早反对推出音乐订阅服务<ref name="Verge: announce"/>，但在{{lang|en|Apple Music}}发布之前，媒体已经预计苹果公司将推出音乐流媒体服务<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/5/13/8603603/apple-music-release-date-social-network|title='Apple Music' service reportedly coming next month with a social network for artists|accessdate=2015-07-24|date=2015-05-13|last=Byford|first=Sam|work=The Verge|archive-date=2015-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723112230/http://www.theverge.com/2015/5/13/8603603/apple-music-release-date-social-network|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Verge: confirmation">{{cite web |url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/7/8742761/apple-music-streaming-launch-confirmation |title=Sony Music boss confirms Apple will reveal its music streaming service tomorrow |accessdate=2015-07-19 |date=2015-06-07 |work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Z8YPEfCf?url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/7/8742761/apple-music-streaming-launch-confirmation |archivedate=2015-06-08 |last1=Plaugic |first1=Lizzie |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2015年6月，[[索尼音乐|索尼音乐]]首席执行官{{le|道格·莫里斯|Doug Morris}}透露苹果公司将在[[苹果公司全球软件开发者年会|全球软件开发者年会]]上宣布推出此项服务<ref name="Verge: confirmation" />。莫里斯还补充称自己希望这项服务能够恢复音乐产业之前的繁荣。他表示另一项音乐流媒体服务{{lang|en|[[Spotify|Spotify]]}}无法在市场上获得利润，因此推广程度也不足；而{{lang|en|Apple Music}}则能大范围推广，进而带动整个音乐流媒体市场的发展。<ref name="Verge: confirmation"/>6月8日，苹果公司正式宣布将推出{{lang|en|Apple Music}}服务<ref name="NYT WWDC"/>。

2015年6月30日，{{lang|en|Apple Music}}在超过100个国家正式发布<ref name="Ars: next chapter"/>。苹果公司最初希望能以较低价格进入市场，然而音乐产业界反对这个计划<ref name="Verge: announce"/>。这项服务随{{lang|en|iOS 8.4}}的更新同时推出，首发时仅供{{lang|en|iOS}}设备、{{lang|en|Apple Watch}}和{{lang|en|iTunes}}用户使用<ref name="Ars: next chapter" /><ref name="apple" /><ref name="TechCrunch" />。美国歌手[[法瑞尔·威廉姆斯|法瑞尔·威廉姆斯]]为{{lang|en|Apple Music}}演唱的宣传歌曲《{{lang|en|Freedom}}》也同时在服务首发时独家发布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2015/06/25/pharrells-new-single-freedom-will-serve-as-apple-musics-first-exclusive/|title=Pharrell's New Single 'Freedom' Will Serve As Apple Music's First Exclusive|accessdate=2015-07-19|date=2015-06-25|last=McIntyre|first=Hugh|publisher=Forbes|archive-date=2015-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801051203/http://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2015/06/25/pharrells-new-single-freedom-will-serve-as-apple-musics-first-exclusive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月30日，此项服务在中国大陆正式上线，个人用户每月收费10元人民币<ref name="iTunes China">{{cite web|url=http://digi.tech.qq.com/a/20150930/020928.htm|title=Apple Music中国正式上线！订阅费每月10元|work=腾讯数码|date=2015-09-30|accessdate=2015-09-30|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003155115/http://digi.tech.qq.com/a/20150930/020928.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chuapp.com/2015/09/30/206749.html|title=中国区Apple Music、iTunes电影、iBooks试用体验|work=触乐网|date=2015-09-30|accessdate=2016-02-05|archive-date=2016-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205162406/http://www.chuapp.com/2015/09/30/206749.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.apple.com/cn/music/membership/|title=会员|work=Apple Music China|accessdate=2016-02-05|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303052156/http://www.apple.com/cn/music/membership/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月10日起，{{lang|en|Apple Music}}客户端在{{lang|en|Google Play}}上架，开始支持{{lang|en|[[Android_4.3|Android 4.3]]}}以上设备<ref name="Android" /><ref name="Android2" />。同年内也开始支持{{lang|en|Apple TV}}<ref name=":1" />。2016年2月4日，{{lang|en|Apple Music}}在土耳其上线<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://macdailynews.com/2016/02/04/apple-music-launches-in-turkey/|title = Apple Music launches in Turkey|last = |first = |date = 2016-02-04|work = Mac Daily News|accessdate = 2016-02-05|archive-date = 2016-02-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160205121249/http://macdailynews.com/2016/02/04/apple-music-launches-in-turkey/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="TR">{{Cite news|url = http://www.ntv.com.tr/teknoloji/apple-music-turkiyede-yayina-girdi,_7GJZUh-wkmTOkFgn-PjqA|title = Apple Music Türkiye'de yayına girdi|last = |first = |date = 2016-02-04|work = NTV|accessdate = 2016-02-05|language = tr|archive-date = 2016-02-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160205052210/http://www.ntv.com.tr/teknoloji/apple-music-turkiyede-yayina-girdi,_7GJZUh-wkmTOkFgn-PjqA|dead-url = no}}</ref>；次日在台湾正式上线，对个人用户每月收费150元[[新台币|新台币]]<ref name="TW">{{cite web|url=http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/22888|title=免費試聽到 5 月！Apple Music 線上音樂在台上線！|work=自由时报|date=2016-02-05|accessdate=2016-02-05|archive-date=2016-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205120814/http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/22888|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://udn.com/news/story/7087/1487800-%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%EF%BC%8FApple-Music%E7%99%BB%E5%8F%B0-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%9A%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%9C%80%E5%A5%BD%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97|title=專訪／Apple Music登台 蘋果：最佳體驗|work=联合新闻网|date=2016-02-05|accessdate=2016-02-05|archive-date=2016-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206080633/http://udn.com/news/story/7087/1487800-%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%EF%BC%8FApple-Music%E7%99%BB%E5%8F%B0-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%9A%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%9C%80%E5%A5%BD%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="iTunes TW">{{cite web|url=http://www.apple.com/tw/music/membership/|title=會員|work=Apple Music Taiwan|accessdate=2016-02-05|archive-date=2016-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205021505/http://www.apple.com/tw/music/membership/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年8月登陆以色列和韩国。<ref name="ISL">{{cite news|title=Apple Music Launches in Israel|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2016/08/03/apple-music-streaming-service-launches-in-israel/|accessdate=2018-04-28|publisher=MacRumors|date=2016-08-03|archive-date=2018-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180428181327/https://www.macrumors.com/2016/08/03/apple-music-streaming-service-launches-in-israel/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ROK">{{cite news|title=Apple Music Launches in South Korea|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2016/08/04/apple-music-launches-in-korea/|accessdate=2018-04-28|publisher=MacRumors|date=2016-08-04|archive-date=2018-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180428181530/https://www.macrumors.com/2016/08/04/apple-music-launches-in-korea/|dead-url=no}}</ref>至此，{{lang|en|Apple Music}}在全球提供服务的国家或地区达到115个。

2016年5月，苹果在美国推出了针对学生的半价订阅计划，<ref>{{cite news |last1=Hardwick |first1=Tim |title=Apple Introduces Apple Music Student Membership Option With 50% Discount at $4.99 per Month |url=https://www.macrumors.com/2016/05/06/apple-music-student-membership-50-discount/ |accessdate=2019-01-25 |work=www.macrumors.com |archive-date=2019-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190125183701/https://www.macrumors.com/2016/05/06/apple-music-student-membership-50-discount/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>之后扩展至32个国家或地区。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Clover |first1=Juli |title=Apple Music Student Pricing Expands to 25 More Countries Around the World |url=https://www.macrumors.com/2016/11/29/apple-music-student-pricing-25-countries/ |accessdate=2019-01-25 |work=www.macrumors.com |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126060820/https://www.macrumors.com/2016/11/29/apple-music-student-pricing-25-countries/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2018年2月25日，{{lang|en|Apple Music}}在香港地區服務將於2月25日加價，涨幅超过20%，最终定价與其主要對手[[Spotify|Spotify]]訂閱費用無異，為服務推出後首個地區及首次加價。<ref>{{cite news |title=香港 Apple Music 下月底加價 $10　最新月費港幣$58 |url=https://unwire.hk/2018/01/27/apple-music-58/mobile-music/ |accessdate=2019-01-25 |work=[[Unwire.hk|Unwire.hk]] |date=2018-01-27 |archive-date=2019-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190125183137/https://unwire.hk/2018/01/27/apple-music-58/mobile-music/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=香港 Apple Music 服務要加價了，加幅超過 20%！ |url=https://qooah.com/2018/01/28/apple-music-hk-price-increase/ |accessdate=2019-01-25 |work=qooah |archive-date=2019-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190125184713/https://qooah.com/2018/01/28/apple-music-hk-price-increase/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

